description:
Hi and welcome back,

Here's the new hybrid live-set of my song 'Texture 06', which is inspired by the first light of spring this year. This time, you can hear beautiful chord progressions from my Blofeld, that I arranged and pre-recorded. Then I used my modular synthesizer to create several melody arrangements, the deep bassline comes from the Neutron and for the sequencers, I used the Hermod and the Keystep. Enjoy listening!

To the song:
https://andreacichecki.bandcamp.com/track/texture-06


Modules & gear I used are:

