@doepfer Envelope, dual Att, performance mixer, random voltages
@behringer Neutron & dual envelope
MFB - Lfo

Pedals used:
@EricaSynths Zen delay & Fusion Box
@ikmultimedia X Delay

Takes from the 'Texture Studies' A sonic exploration by Andrea CicheckiThis is the sixth track in a series of ‘Texture Studies’, performed live and recorded in one take. It’s research in programming and patching, combined with creative experiments, playing with time, space and letting go of song forms and structures. It’s about creating sound-collages that make you see the sounds and textures like a painting. I will perform this series throughout the year, with a live-video and a release of each track.

